Energy Corporation, TXU and Xenergy Inc. 

Our distinguished panelists at this year's Forum will examine: 

Crisis 2001: Strategies in stress?
Has the deregulation train derailed??
Restructuring strategies for value creation & growth?
Looking past the turbulence-where will the money be made?

